Workload Manager (WLM) manages how many concurrent stored procedures can run in an
address space and thenumber of concurrent stored procedures in an address space
cannot exceed the value of the NUMTCB parameter. Which statement about the value of
NUMTCB is correct?
A. NUMTCB parameter must be set to 1 for Java stored procedures.
B. NUMTCB parameter must beset to 1 for REXX stored procedures.
C. NUMTCB parameter can be a value greater than 1 for native SQL stored procedures.
D. NUMTCB parameter can be a value greater than 1 when a stored procedure invokes
DB2 utilities.
Answer: B
